flowchart TD
    A[Create order] --> B[Store target, side, size]
    B --> C[Resolve trigger direction]
    C --> D[Scanner checks fresh market data]
    D --> E{Target reached?}
    E -->|No| D
    E -->|Yes| F[Claim order]
    F --> G[Probe live route]
    G --> H{Target output satisfied?}
    H -->|No| I[Release and keep watching]
    H -->|Yes| J[Create execution quote]
    J --> K[Execute swap]
    K --> L[Update order status]

